00:48:54.629 --> 00:48:58.564
(ECHOES FAINTLY) But God has
given you a second life.

499
00:48:58.566 --> 00:49:02.468
(ECHOES INCREASE)
I know all your pain.

500
00:49:02.470 --> 00:49:06.406
I'll guide you
through the darkness

501
00:49:06.408 --> 00:49:08.709
to the light.

502
00:49:08.711 --> 00:49:12.446
and find the soul
that belongs to you.

503
00:49:12.448 --> 00:49:15.683
Love is all around you.

504
00:49:15.685 --> 00:49:18.822
(INTRIGUING MUSIC BUILDS)

505
00:49:39.876 --> 00:49:42.109
(DARK MUSIC)

506
00:49:42.111 --> 00:49:43.410
- No! No!
- (ZAP!)

507
00:49:43.412 --> 00:49:46.913
- Everybody get out!
- (SCREAMING)

508
00:49:46.915 --> 00:49:51.053
(DARK MUSIC BUILDS)

509
00:49:52.689 --> 00:49:54.754
- (YELLING AND SCREAMING)
- Stop!

510
00:49:54.756 --> 00:49:56.626
Don't kill the innocent people.

511
00:50:02.432 --> 00:50:04.163
Hey! I got this!

512
00:50:04.165 --> 00:50:07.303
(MUSIC INTENSIFIES. THEN FADES)

513
00:50:12.975 --> 00:50:14.607
COSENTINO: You are late.

514
00:50:14.609 --> 00:50:17.513
- (KNIFE RINGS)
- (COSENTINO GRUNTS)

515
00:50:19.649 --> 00:50:21.381
My work here is done.

516
00:50:21.383 --> 00:50:23.452
- (KNIFE HISSES)
- (GRUNTS)

517
00:50:25.588 --> 00:50:27.921
Put your weapons down!
Get on the ground!

518
00:50:27.923 --> 00:50:30.457
(GUNFIRE)

519
00:50:30.459 --> 00:50:33.596
(EXCITING MUSIC)

520
00:50:40.870 --> 00:50:42.472
(GASPS)

521
00:51:08.865 --> 00:51:10.567
(YELLS)

522
00:51:12.901 --> 00:51:14.436
Get him.

523
00:51:35.258 --> 00:51:36.826
Kill him.

524
00:52:10.258 --> 00:52:12.060
Pick me up at the entrance.

525
00:52:20.970 --> 00:52:24.203
You know. you're really starting
to piss me off.

526
00:52:24.205 --> 00:52:25.973
Give me back my daughter.

527
00:52:25.975 --> 00:52:27.674
You want her?

528
00:52:27.676 --> 00:52:29.646
She's all yours. Daddy.

529
00:52:31.513 --> 00:52:33.082
(BLADES CLANK)

530
00:52:36.218 --> 00:52:38.417
- (BLADES WHIRR)
- (YELLS)

531
00:52:38.419 --> 00:52:41.691
(BLADES CHIME)

532
00:52:43.559 --> 00:52:45.861
(LIFT BELL RINGS)

533
00:52:57.573 --> 00:52:59.475
(LIFT BELL RINGS)

534
00:53:00.676 --> 00:53:03.847
(GOOFY MUSIC)

535
00:53:06.348 --> 00:53:09.017
(TENSE MUSIC)

536
00:53:30.138 --> 00:53:33.108
(MUSIC BUILDS)

537
00:54:04.372 --> 00:54:07.543
(BLADES CLANK)

538
00:54:10.845 --> 00:54:13.615
(TENSE MUSIC BUILDS)

539
00:54:56.425 --> 00:54:59.595
(METAL SNAPS)

540
00:55:04.399 --> 00:55:06.301
(CABLE CREAKS)

541
00:55:14.609 --> 00:55:17.611
(YELLS)

542
00:55:17.613 --> 00:55:20.750
(MUSIC BUILDS)

543
00:55:22.551 --> 00:55:24.654
(GRUNTS)

544
00:55:30.593 --> 00:55:33.229
(YELLS)

545
00:55:36.231 --> 00:55:37.497
(YELLS)

546
00:55:37.499 --> 00:55:39.700
(BLADES WHOOSH. THEN TING)

547
00:55:39.702 --> 00:55:41.634
Ohhh! Oh!

548
00:55:41.636 --> 00:55:44.740
(TENSE MUSIC BUILDS)

549
00:55:48.209 --> 00:55:49.978
(YELLS)

550
00:55:54.450 --> 00:55:57.783
(QUIRKY MUSIC)

551
00:55:57.785 --> 00:56:00.389
Sorry. (SLURPS)

552
00:56:02.591 --> 00:56:04.323
(SIGHS)

553
00:56:04.325 --> 00:56:07.262
(FOREBODING MUSIC)

554
00:56:14.636 --> 00:56:17.807
(TENSE MUSIC BUILDS)

555
00:56:28.149 --> 00:56:30.052
Yaaah!

556
00:56:32.021 --> 00:56:33.923
Yaaaah!

557
00:57:29.778 --> 00:57:31.947
(HANDCUFFS CLINK)

558
00:57:39.455 --> 00:57:41.157
(ELECTRONIC BEEPING)

559
00:58:18.426 --> 00:58:21.396
(STEADY BEEPING)

560
00:59:21.689 --> 00:59:23.358
(BEEPING STOPS)

561
00:59:52.921 --> 00:59:56.091
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN
OVER PHONE)

562
01:00:04.533 --> 01:00:07.502
(LIN SPEAKS MANDARIN)

563
01:00:12.640 --> 01:00:15.040
(DOOR CREAKS)

564
01:00:15.042 --> 01:00:19.281
- (DISQUIETING MUSIC)
- (GUN CLICKS)

565
01:00:27.990 --> 01:00:31.160
(BELL TOLLS DISTANTLY)

566
01:00:40.702 --> 01:00:42.170
Hello?

567
01:00:43.872 --> 01:00:46.008
Hello?

568
01:00:54.515 --> 01:00:56.351
H...

569
01:01:32.254 --> 01:01:34.386
- (SIGHS)
- (WATCH CHIMES)

570
01:01:34.388 --> 01:01:37.524
(WATCH BEEPS STEADILY)

571
01:01:37.526 --> 01:01:42.529
(ENGINE ROARS. TYRES SCREECH)

572
01:01:42.531 --> 01:01:45.468
(TENSE MUSIC)

573
01:01:52.807 --> 01:01:55.243
(DOOR SQUEAKS)

574
01:02:14.897 --> 01:02:18.067
(LEESON SPEAKS MANDARIN)

575
01:02:26.575 --> 01:02:29.609
(WHISTLES THEN SOBS)

576
01:02:29.611 --> 01:02:31.513
(TENSE MUSIC)

577
01:02:46.694 --> 01:02:49.664
(PENSIVE MUSIC)

578
01:03:13.254 --> 01:03:15.721
DR JAMES: She must be protected.

579
01:03:15.723 --> 01:03:20.225
- (MACHINE BEEPS STEADILY)
- All my work is in her body.

580
01:03:20.227 --> 01:03:22.194
Someday she'll be the proof
to the world

581
01:03:22.196 --> 01:03:24.397
of my contribution to mankind.

582
01:03:24.399 --> 01:03:26.868
(MACHINE BEEPS STEADILY)

583
01:03:32.540 --> 01:03:35.711
(MACHINE EMITS CONTINUOUS BEEP)

584
01:03:44.852 --> 01:03:47.822
(LIN AND SUSAN SPEAK MANDARIN)

585
01:04:32.968 --> 01:04:35.868
(ELECTRONIC BEEPING)

586
01:04:35.870 --> 01:04:38.807
(MUSIC BUILDS)

587
01:04:53.888 --> 01:04:56.858
Oh. (CHUCKLES)

588
01:05:11.573 --> 01:05:13.676
(GRUNTS)

589
01:05:19.914 --> 01:05:22.884
(MUSIC INTENSIFIES)

590
01:05:25.787 --> 01:05:27.223
(GRUNTS)

591
01:05:28.222 --> 01:05:30.323
(ELECTRONIC BEEPING)

592
01:05:30.325 --> 01:05:31.760
(CAR ALARMS BLARE)

593
01:05:41.035 --> 01:05:44.005
(SCREAMS)

594
01:05:54.515 --> 01:05:57.019
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN)

595
01:06:45.334 --> 01:06:47.366
(SIGHS)

596
01:06:47.368 --> 01:06:48.736
(SOMBRE MUSIC)

597
01:07:43.158 --> 01:07:46.127
(CAR ENGINE PURRS)

598
01:07:48.129 --> 01:07:51.099
(UPBEAT PIANO MUSIC)

599
01:07:53.535 --> 01:07:58.006
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN)

600
01:08:38.413 --> 01:08:40.582
(WATCH BEEPS)

601
01:08:47.588 --> 01:08:49.624
(ENGINE ROARS)

602
01:09:07.141 --> 01:09:09.110
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN)

603
01:09:30.397 --> 01:09:33.569
(UNEASY MUSIC)

604
01:09:44.479 --> 01:09:46.511
(DOOR SQUEAKS)

605
01:09:46.513 --> 01:09:49.650
(FOREBODING MUSIC)

606
01:09:58.592 --> 01:10:01.762
(EERIE WHOOSHING)

607
01:10:22.316 --> 01:10:25.287
(TROUBLING MUSIC)

608
01:10:30.124 --> 01:10:31.827
Trust me.

609
01:10:33.028 --> 01:10:34.562
Hello.

610
01:10:43.771 --> 01:10:45.670
All my work is in her body.

611
01:10:45.672 --> 01:10:48.474
Every detail is recorded
in her blood.

612
01:10:48.476 --> 01:10:50.076
She must be protected.

613
01:10:50.078 --> 01:10:52.411
Someday she'll be the proof
to the world

614
01:10:52.413 --> 01:10:54.279
of my contribution to mankind.

615
01:10:54.281 --> 01:10:57.218
(SOMBRE MUSIC)

616
01:11:11.333 --> 01:11:14.269
(WISTFUL MUSIC)

617
01:12:05.052 --> 01:12:07.622
(SOBS)

618
01:12:12.394 --> 01:12:14.162
(FOOTSTEPS APPROACH)

619
01:12:15.430 --> 01:12:18.133
(GRIM MUSIC)

620
01:12:19.434 --> 01:12:21.332
(ENGINE GROWLS)

621
01:12:21.334 --> 01:12:23.038
(WATCH BEEPS)

622
01:12:33.147 --> 01:12:35.150
(TYRES SCREECH)

623
01:13:05.145 --> 01:13:06.447
Ugh!

624
01:13:18.126 --> 01:13:20.995
I don't have time for this.

625
01:13:24.598 --> 01:13:27.769
- (GRUNTS)
- (DRAMATIC MUSIC)

626
01:14:27.561 --> 01:14:29.797
(METAL SCRAPES)

627
01:14:34.936 --> 01:14:36.438
(SHOUTS IN MANDARIN)

628
01:14:41.508 --> 01:14:44.412
- (GASPS)
- (BRAKES SCREECH)

629
01:14:59.459 --> 01:15:02.029
(TYRES SCREECH)

630
01:15:03.096 --> 01:15:04.498
(PANTS)

631
01:15:25.720 --> 01:15:27.719
(PHONE BEEPS)

632
01:15:27.721 --> 01:15:30.124
(LEESON SPEAKS MANDARIN)

633
01:16:01.455 --> 01:16:03.522
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN
ON PHONE)

634
01:16:03.524 --> 01:16:05.327
(ENGINE FALSE STARTS)

635
01:16:10.597 --> 01:16:13.133
(SNIGGERS AND MUTTERS)

636
01:16:18.205 --> 01:16:20.275
WOMAN: Good afternoon.
May I help you?

637
01:16:27.080 --> 01:16:28.949
MAN: Please wait a minute.

638
01:16:44.998 --> 01:16:47.601
Thank you. This way. please.

639
01:17:01.449 --> 01:17:03.618
(ZAPPING)

640
01:17:06.154 --> 01:17:08.323
(VEHICLE HORNS HONK)

641
01:17:46.194 --> 01:17:47.729
(DOOR CLANGS)

642
01:17:51.498 --> 01:17:54.234
No. no. no. no!
Bastard! (GRUNTS)

643
01:17:55.570 --> 01:17:57.238
(WEAPONS CLICK)

644
01:18:02.043 --> 01:18:05.146
- (TYRES SCREECH)
- (PEOPLE SCREAM)

645
01:18:31.806 --> 01:18:33.375
(DOOR LOCK BEEPS)

646
01:18:38.745 --> 01:18:40.614
(GAS HISSES)

647
01:19:11.212 --> 01:19:15.383
(ALARM BEEPS)

648
01:19:54.122 --> 01:19:56.624
(VIDEO CAMERA BEEPS)

649
01:20:04.565 --> 01:20:06.631
DR JAMES IN VIDEO: <i>Such superior
regeneration ability</i>

650
01:20:06.633 --> 01:20:09.902
<i>is attributed to the activation
of the regenerative genes</i>

651
01:20:09.904 --> 01:20:12.371
<i>from the starfish.</i>

652
01:20:12.373 --> 01:20:15.607
<i>Each recombined cell contains
the entire genome</i>

653
01:20:15.609 --> 01:20:17.442
<i>and fuses to other tissues</i>

654
01:20:17.444 --> 01:20:20.746
<i>to rapidly regrow
the missing part.</i>

655
01:20:20.748 --> 01:20:23.148
<i>The experimental subject
is a special force</i>

656
01:20:23.150 --> 01:20:26.684
<i>exposed to heavy
nuclear radiation.</i>

657
01:20:26.686 --> 01:20:28.886
<i>He'll become the first
biowarrior in the world</i>

658
01:20:28.888 --> 01:20:30.592
<i>if the experiment succeeds.</i>

659
01:20:32.325 --> 01:20:35.059
- (SAW WHIRRS)
- (SCREAMS AND GRUNTS)

660
01:20:35.061 --> 01:20:37.698
(PANTS)

661
01:20:39.934 --> 01:20:42.302
(GROANS AND PANTS)

662
01:20:45.672 --> 01:20:47.541
(STOPS GROANING)

663
01:20:56.050 --> 01:20:58.116
DR JAMES: <i>We have developed
the first-generation</i>

664
01:20:58.118 --> 01:21:00.152
<i>mechanical heart to match</i>

665
01:21:00.154 --> 01:21:03.455
<i>the rapid regeneration feature
of the bioengineered blood.</i>

666
01:21:03.457 --> 01:21:05.924
<i>If the experiment succeeds.
the bioroid.</i>

667
01:21:05.926 --> 01:21:08.327
<i>with the mechanical heart
and the bioengineered blood.</i>

668
01:21:08.329 --> 01:21:11.466
<i>will be the immortal warrior
of the future.</i>

669
01:22:20.935 --> 01:22:22.736
Yes. madam.

670
01:22:48.029 --> 01:22:49.661
Hey. boss. they're back.

671
01:22:49.663 --> 01:22:51.966
- (SCREEN BEEPS)
- (MACHINERY WHIRRS)

672
01:22:56.537 --> 01:22:59.406
MAN: You and I
are actually the same.

673
01:23:01.074 --> 01:23:05.412
We're lab rats
in his little experiments.

674
01:23:08.748 --> 01:23:13.184
Ah. the only difference is
you didn't get to experience

675
01:23:13.186 --> 01:23:15.589
the pain that I've suffered.

676
01:23:17.190 --> 01:23:20.892
That sly fox.

677
01:23:20.894 --> 01:23:24.699
Hiding his life's work
inside of you.

678
01:23:29.302 --> 01:23:34.309
And all these years
just to find you.

679
01:23:36.877 --> 01:23:40.312
I feel like you've turned me
into a monster.

680
01:23:40.314 --> 01:23:42.617
(LAUGHS)

681
01:23:46.454 --> 01:23:48.823
(ENGINES RUMBLE)

682
01:23:59.800 --> 01:24:03.003
- (EQUIPMENT HISSES)
- (PANTS)

683
01:24:06.806 --> 01:24:08.673
COMPUTER VOICE:
<i>Diverter initiated.</i>

684
01:24:08.675 --> 01:24:10.677
<i>Purification in process.</i>

685
01:24:13.012 --> 01:24:16.617
- (FLUIDS SQUELCH)
- (EQUIPMENT WHIRRS)

686
01:24:28.162 --> 01:24:29.997
Who are you? Oh...

687
01:24:31.030 --> 01:24:32.667
(GROANS)

688
01:24:33.868 --> 01:24:36.100
We have the same
mechanical heart.

689
01:24:36.102 --> 01:24:39.640
But I'm getting eaten alive
by my own cells.

690
01:24:41.175 --> 01:24:43.774
Thanks to Dr James's blood.

691
01:24:43.776 --> 01:24:46.344
not only will I get
my powers back

692
01:24:46.346 --> 01:24:51.950
but your blood will give me
the ability to regenerate.

693
01:24:51.952 --> 01:24:55.754
The world's first
super biowarrior.

694
01:24:55.756 --> 01:25:00.828
My blood contains two sets
of memories for 13 years.

695
01:25:02.997 --> 01:25:04.728
Those painful memories

696
01:25:04.730 --> 01:25:07.135
constantly tortured me
day by day.

697
01:25:09.803 --> 01:25:14.107
You will have three memories
once I pass them on to you.

698
01:25:15.443 --> 01:25:18.980
And believe me.
you will go insane.

699
01:25:20.013 --> 01:25:22.182
(HALF-LAUGHS) No.

700
01:25:23.217 --> 01:25:25.649
You see this diverter here?

701
01:25:25.651 --> 01:25:29.254
It'll remove all the impurities
in your blood.

702
01:25:29.256 --> 01:25:33.194
Never again will I experience
any more pain.

703
01:26:09.096 --> 01:26:11.161
- (WEAPON RINGS)
- Where's the Asian girl?

704
01:26:11.163 --> 01:26:13.767
- In... inside the lab.
- Open the door.

705
01:26:18.672 --> 01:26:20.842
(EQUIPMENT BEEPS AND CHIMES)

706
01:26:24.278 --> 01:26:26.079
What are you guys doing?

707
01:26:27.847 --> 01:26:30.648
- Nancy.
- Where do you think you're going?

708
01:26:30.650 --> 01:26:33.117
- Arrgh!
- Shaun! Sound the alarm!

709
01:26:33.119 --> 01:26:35.789
- (OTHERS SHOUT)
- Get outta here! Go. go. go. go!

710
01:26:37.658 --> 01:26:39.491
Nancy! Nancy!

711
01:26:39.493 --> 01:26:42.062
Nan... Oh!

712
01:26:43.931 --> 01:26:45.732
Nancy.

713
01:26:47.700 --> 01:26:49.600
- Nancy.
- Nancy!

714
01:26:49.602 --> 01:26:51.771
- (SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN)
- Nancy!

715
01:27:00.647 --> 01:27:02.650
(SUSAN SPEAKS MANDARIN)

716
01:27:17.664 --> 01:27:20.133
(INAUDIBLE)

717
01:27:25.538 --> 01:27:27.706
(GRUNTS)

718
01:27:27.708 --> 01:27:30.041
- (GRUNTS)
- Arrgh! (GROANS)

719
01:27:30.043 --> 01:27:32.313
- Open it!
- Only the boss can do that.

720
01:27:59.373 --> 01:28:01.208
(SUSAN GRUNTS)

721
01:28:02.242 --> 01:28:04.278
(DOOR WHIZZES)

722
01:28:07.580 --> 01:28:09.150
(GRUNTS)

723
01:28:22.395 --> 01:28:24.264
(GRUNTS)

724
01:28:35.309 --> 01:28:37.011
- (BEEP)
- (GRUNTS)

725
01:28:54.528 --> 01:28:56.830
- (DRAMATIC MUSIC)
- (GRUNTS)

726
01:29:40.606 --> 01:29:42.443
(GRUNTS)

727
01:29:45.378 --> 01:29:47.314
(GRUNTS)

728
01:29:54.253 --> 01:29:56.122
(GRUNTS)

729
01:30:06.667 --> 01:30:08.302
(GRUNTS)

730
01:30:14.775 --> 01:30:17.075
- Ugh!
- Arrgh!

731
01:30:17.077 --> 01:30:19.312
Arrgh!

732
01:30:23.516 --> 01:30:25.385
(GROANS)

733
01:30:29.922 --> 01:30:32.992
I'm gonna enjoy killing you.

734
01:30:40.801 --> 01:30:42.666
Ugh!

735
01:30:42.668 --> 01:30:44.469
(GROANS)

736
01:30:44.471 --> 01:30:47.471
(SHOUTS AND GRUNTS)

737
01:30:47.473 --> 01:30:50.410
Ahh! Huh?

738
01:30:51.611 --> 01:30:53.513
(GRUNTING)

739
01:30:56.083 --> 01:30:57.084
(GRUNTS)

740
01:31:03.123 --> 01:31:04.759
(GRUNTS)

741
01:31:05.825 --> 01:31:08.194
- (SUSAN GRUNTS)
- (LEESON SHOUTS)

742
01:31:09.562 --> 01:31:11.429
(GRUNTS)

743
01:31:11.431 --> 01:31:13.497
Yah! Huh? (MUTTERS)

744
01:31:13.499 --> 01:31:15.834
(SHOUTS AND GRUNTS)

745
01:31:15.836 --> 01:31:18.469
(GRUNTS) Arrgh!

746
01:31:18.471 --> 01:31:20.841
(GRUNTS REPEATEDLY)

747
01:31:23.177 --> 01:31:25.012
(GROANS)

748
01:31:33.287 --> 01:31:35.789
(GRUNTS)

749
01:31:37.391 --> 01:31:39.193
(SOMBRE MUSIC)

750
01:31:56.443 --> 01:31:58.475
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

751
01:31:58.477 --> 01:32:00.510
COMPUTER VOICE: <i>Blood
transfusion interrupted.</i>

752
01:32:00.512 --> 01:32:02.015
<i>Reverting.</i>

753
01:32:20.633 --> 01:32:22.602
(SNIFFS AND GRUNTS SOFTLY)

